Arkansas River, shedding their blue jackets while they chatted with 
the casually dressed farmers about an array of problems, including 
subsidized rice from Japan and subsidized cotton from China. Both 
crops are grown in Arkansas. 
</P>
<P>
	Gore proclaimed the current farm bill ``badly broken'' and  
