<DOCNO> APW19990807.0116 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-07 17:10:09 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Gary Grant Signs With Blazers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) -- Gary Grant signed a one-year contract with  
the Portland Trail Blazers today. 
</P>
<P>
	Terms weren't disclosed.  
</P>
<P>
	Grant, 34, has played 11 seasons in the NBA including stints  
with the Los Angeles Clippers, New York and Miami. He has spent 
part of each of the last two seasons with Portland. 
</P>
<P>
	In 24 games with Portland, Grant averaged 4.4 points and 3.7  
assists with an 85.7 free-throw percentage. 
</P>
<P>
	The 6-foot-3 Grant was selected by Seattle in the first round of  
the 1988 draft and was traded to the Clippers for Michael Cage. 
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
